    What color is razzmatazz?
    An AI Overview is not available for this searchCan't generate an AI overview right now. Try again later.
    AI Overview
    Razzmatazz is a vibrant, eye-catching shade of pinkish-red, or crimson-rose. It is an energetic and bold color that falls between red and magenta on the color wheel. 
    • Description: Razzmatazz is a bright, vivid, and saturated pinkish-red color. 
    • Color Wheel: It is positioned between red and magenta. 
    • Origin: The name was introduced by Crayola in 1993 through a "Name The New Colors Contest" and was first suggested by a 5-year-old. 
    • Hex Code: The hexadecimal color code is #E3256B.
